[30;1m73 | [0m[35mthe isapi package is installed next to the script, and IIS configured to[0m
[30;1m74 | [0m[35muse this DLL.[0m
[30;1m75 | [0m[35m<p>[0m

[30;1m140 | [0m[35mdef RegisterModule(modName, modPath):[0m
[30;1m141 | [0m[35m    """Register an explicit module in the registry.  This forces the Python import[0m
[30;1m142 | [0m[35m    mechanism to locate this module directly, without a sys.path search.  Thus[0m
[30;1m143 | [0m[35m    a registered module need not appear in sys.path at all.[0m
[30;1m144 | [0m[35m[0m
